<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ClarityPMDD</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #f5c6ec, #b7d5e5); /* Example gradient */
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .header-section {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 5rem 1rem;
            background: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .header-section h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .header-section p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .btn-start {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            border: 1px solid #2c3e50;
            background: transparent;
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: background 0.3s, color 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-start:hover {
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .feature-section {
            padding: 4rem 1rem;
            background-color: #355d73;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .feature-section h2 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .feature-item {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .feature-item img {
            width: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .feature-item p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Header Section -->
    <section class="header-section">
        <h1>ClarityPMDD</h1>
        <p>A personalized tool to help you track, and navigate your cycle with confidence.</p>
        <p class="text-muted">Your cycle, your insights.</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-start">Start Tracking</a>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Content Section -->
    <section class="container my-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2>When it comes to your cycle, ClarityPMDD is your guide.</h2>
                <p>Track the symptoms that matter most to you and uncover meaningful patterns with personalized insights. ClarityPMDD helps you navigate each phase of your cycle with confidence and control.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img src="abstract-image.png" alt="Abstract Cycle Image" class="img-fluid rounded-circle">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section class="feature-section">
        <h2>ClarityPMDD Features</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 feature-item">
                <img src="icon1.png" alt="Customizable Tracking Icon">
                <p>Track only the symptoms and emotions that matter to you, with flexible options that fit your unique experience.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 feature-item">
                <img src="icon2.png" alt="Easy Input Icon">
                <p>Designed for simplicity, ClarityPMDD lets you log your symptoms quickly, making consistent tracking easy over time.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 feature-item">
                <img src="icon3.png" alt="Visualize Patterns Icon">
                <p>Turn your data into graphs that reveal cycles and patterns in your emotions and physical well-being.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
